extendedInfo.description: Fancy Jigsaw is a classic puzzle game. Drag the posterspieces to the right place to re-establish the full picture. Don't sweat it if you are unable to solve the puzzle easily. You can use the peek button to preview the original image.There are 100 levels in this game. The further you advance, the more challenging the puzzle becomes. This app also allows you to save the MMO Game posters to your SD .Still missing the days as group member fight via boss, or PK other team in WOW raid?If you are a fan of MMORPG, you wonât miss this app, filled with game posters of human, warrior, priest, angel, huntress, archer, dwarf, orc, blood elf, download and enjoy!Cool Features Include:- More than 100 pictures of MMO Game posters- Multiple difficulty levels (from 3*3 to the most difficult 7*7).- Save to phone album function.- Images gallery and difficulty selection.Fancy JigSaw is suitable for a wide range of audiences, Many different modes and pictures in the game will keep you excited and entertained for a long time.Keywords:puzzle,puzzles,Jigsaw,games,brainfun,funny,Game Art posters,entertainment,wallpapers
